    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>爬到顶端！</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9b862b5061b3119e902cf1acc8ed3033.poster.avif?t=1746467243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9b862b5061b3119e902cf1acc8ed3033.webm?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9b862b5061b3119e902cf1acc8ed3033.mp4?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Green Heights</strong> 是一个第一人称垂直精度平台游戏，具有流畅和令人满意的移动。在一个独特的类似于生态瓶的环境中，攀登塔楼并达到顶端。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>重新站起来。</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/2c47085a299a62936b0871c2eb77cc86.poster.avif?t=1746467243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/2c47085a299a62936b0871c2eb77cc86.webm?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/2c47085a299a62936b0871c2eb77cc86.mp4?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跌倒是不可避免的，每一个错误都是一个教训，你可以利用这些教训来爬得更快。塔内有许多捷径，发现它们以打破你的个人最佳成绩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9d8eb4439dedb913cd3f00351e487c28.poster.avif?t=1746467243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9d8eb4439dedb913cd3f00351e487c28.webm?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9d8eb4439dedb913cd3f00351e487c28.mp4?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >流畅且反应迅速的移动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大气的生态瓶植被</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跑步、跳跃、攀爬和反弹到顶端</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现捷径</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >排行榜</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幽灵 PB</p></li></ul>",
